areas.name: Area_55
areas.callback:
function(self)
  local lv,dd,ff,book = TrackInformation("NHB21T",self)
  if book~=BookType.RouteLock or ff==false then
    return
  end

  local k=GetLeftTrackArea("NHB21T",self)
  if lv=="NHB11R" or lv=="NHB12R" then
    SendRightAxle(self,{25,4})
  elseif lv=="NHB11L" or lv=="NHB12L" then
    SendLeftAxle(self,{25,4})
  elseif lv=="NHB4L" or lv=="NHB5L" then
    SendLeftAxle(self,{50,4})
  elseif lv=="NHB4R" and  k and #(k.axles)>0 then
    SendRightAxle(self,{50,4})
  elseif lv=="NHB4R" or lv=="NHB5R" then
    if LEVERS["WAK1R"].aspect >= 2 then
      SendRightAxle(self,{110,4})
    else
      SendRightAxle(self,{50,4})
    end
  end
end
